> 55 minutes ago, manghoti said:
> 
> 
> Is there a way to filter out LDEF science from Field Research?
> 

To get Field Research to ignore certain experiment types you can add a Module Manager patch file to your GameData folder. Copy the below code into a blank text file and save it with a .cfg extension in order to get FR to ignore all WBI experiments:

Spoiler

CC_EXPERIMENT_DEFINITIONS
    {
        name = WBILDEF

        EXPERIMENT
        {
            name = WBIBRE
            ignored = true
        }

        EXPERIMENT
        {
            name = WBISAME
            ignored = true
        }EXPERIMENT
